17. Simple explanation of each stage

Clone

Jenkins downloads project from GitHub.

Build Image

Jenkins builds Docker image using Dockerfile.

Push Image

Jenkins pushes image to Docker Hub.

Deploy Container

Jenkins runs container from that image.


